R. Rick Hart 
Executive Compensation
As Executive Vice President at RENASANT CORP, R. Rick Hart  made $929,524 in total compensation.  Of this total $496,000 was received as a salary, $158,392 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $217,840 was awarded as stock and $57,292 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


